getDimensionHref

public final java.lang.String getDimensionHref(int width,
                                               int height)
Get the HREF to retrieve an image with specific width-height dimensions. A HTTP request using this HREF will return the image data.

Parameters:
width - The image width.
height - The image height.
Returns:
The HREF to retrieve the image with the specified width-height dimensions. Can be null if an image with the specified dimensions is unavailable.
